"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"On January 21st, IOHK, the parent company of Cardano, announced a major scale update on Twitter, which means that Plutusâ€™ script storage units will increase to 12.5 million. The initial changes will take effect on January 25, 5 days after the update proposal process begins. Improving Plutus' memory/CPU parameters remains one of 11 ways Cardano plans to scale in 2022. Other paths include block size increase, Pipelining, Input Endorsers, node augmentation, disk storage, sidechains, Layer 2 Hydra scaling solution, offload computation, and Mithril solution.\",\"timestamp\":1642731097,\"title\":\"Cardano is about to get a major update, adding Plutus script storage units\"},\"digest\":\"Ffa2f7F9ee6jChXjiqP-0d9rfcAgOvoGt3agLceTTJI\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x6747C8bD7EaC2C5b2e2999cF44257719Fac5ac4d\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"EkH8tu12MRRE20C-AO5X9pSygOOCKxrZ8BaWlSjp6DU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"qXWSv706HFjI2U-_tKoTkmC2kPuuO1CFhyWPkgVGVBw\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"aQfOroZtauwdsgVP_DABbHb0VvpPcnpdP_Ticf6Osgln6WwTVQLfDnDkE0JZPL3bIvqFO6GFawClmnbATEAXyg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xdf2dc6bc4c2f085221102e01c4b8e2fea01d6271c20bac65b4983d91ed909592546b8eb248fb4ee4e9f08c17052a6efd48d391ebd40930d14652b3a4dc5367ad1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"EkH8tu12MRRE20C-AO5X9pSygOOCKxrZ8BaWlSjp6DU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"qXWSv706HFjI2U-_tKoTkmC2kPuuO1CFhyWPkgVGVBw\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"Ffa2f7F9ee6jChXjiqP-0d9rfcAgOvoGt3agLceTTJI\"}"